00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:55,340
we should be good here, I think.

244
00:11:55,340 --> 00:11:56,790
And you got to pick one here.

245
00:12:00,140 --> 00:12:00,640
Very good.

246
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:03,370
Can we have a coin toss please?

247
00:12:03,370 --> 00:12:04,300
AUDIENCE: Heads.

248
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:05,460
PROFESSOR: Heads again.

249
00:12:05,460 --> 00:12:07,560
What do we got?

250
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:08,480
All right, good job.

251
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:11,506
OK, Adam got heads and
