843
00:40:44,310 --> 00:40:48,177
x in the range of x times
of probability R equals x.

844
00:40:48,177 --> 00:40:49,760
And that's what I
was trying to prove.

845
00:40:55,870 --> 00:41:00,990
OK, any questions about that?

846
00:41:00,990 --> 00:41:03,230
Now there are some
special cases of this

