failure is what?

972
00:50:54,510 --> 00:50:55,322
100.

973
00:50:55,322 --> 00:50:57,260
1 over 0.01.

974
00:50:57,260 --> 00:51:01,870
So very easy to compute
mean time to failure.

975
00:51:01,870 --> 00:51:06,264
Any questions about that?

976
00:51:06,264 --> 00:51:08,430
Of course, you can do it
with the other definitions,

977
00:51:08,430 --> 00:51:11,660
