01:13:54,970 --> 01:13:57,940
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
sets, like when

1393
01:13:57,940 --> 01:14:01,845
we're looking at the failure.

1394
01:14:01,845 --> 01:14:06,208
Couldn't we add the two
