1402
01:14:25,310 --> 01:14:26,760
because you got a boy or a girl.

1403
01:14:26,760 --> 01:14:28,330
One of them had to happen.

1404
01:14:28,330 --> 01:14:29,920
And the expected
value would be one,

1405
01:14:29,920 --> 01:14:32,690
But that's a different
kind of game.

1406
01:14:32,690 --> 01:14:36,440
But we are going to start using
