1476
01:18:50,830 --> 01:18:52,710
So it's an indicator
random variable.

1477
01:18:52,710 --> 01:18:59,610
It's 1 if the ith man
gets the right hat.

1478
01:19:02,170 --> 01:19:04,110
And it's 0 if he doesn't.

1479
01:19:10,060 --> 01:19:14,700
So whenever the ith guy gets his
